visual.name: TableHeatMap
visual.description: You can use this custom visual to build a table heat map that can be used to visualise and compare data values in an easy and intuitive way. You have a built-in option within this visual to specify the number of buckets used for splitting your data. Additionally, you can also customise it by choosing a colour scheme in line with your brand colours
